bilingual.source: Reagan played a key role in ending the Cold War.
bilingual.target: 里根在结束冷战中发挥了关键作用。

bilingual.source: The movie finishes up with a surprising ending.
bilingual.target: 这部电影结束于一个令人惊讶的结局。

bilingual.source: The peace pacts were crucial for ending the conflict.
bilingual.target: 和平协议对于结束冲突至关重要。

bilingual.source: We need a better ending to conclude this article.
bilingual.target: 我们需要一个更好的结尾来结束这篇文章。

bilingual.source: The batter flied to right field, ending the game.
bilingual.target: 击球手击球出局，球飞向右外野，比赛结束。

bilingual.source: He failed in this election, ending his political life.
bilingual.target: 他在这次选举中失败，结束了他的政治生命。

bilingual.source: The abolitionist spoke passionately about ending slavery.
bilingual.target: 这位废奴主义者激情洋溢地谈论着结束奴隶制。

bilingual.source: The Sui dynasty unified the Northern and Southern Dynasties, ending a long period of division.
bilingual.target: 隋朝统一了南北朝，结束了长期的分裂局面。

bilingual.source: Kissinger received the Nobel Peace Prize in 1973 for his efforts in ending the Vietnam War.
bilingual.target: 基辛格因其结束越南战争的努力于1973年获得诺贝尔和平奖。

list.abstract: 专辑的每首歌背后又有着有趣的故事，每一首歌都凝聚着唱片公司诚意和SHE的努力，整张专辑听下来让没有了生气的耳朵顿生欣喜而难以割舍。
《Ending》是鲍文洋2015年发行的专辑，共2首歌曲。

yingyinNormal.en: I did not see that common twist ending. My stories never end like that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有出人意料的结局, 我的故事从来不会这样结束。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know, but apparently I'm in some kind of relationship, and you seem to be an expert at ending them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道但显然我陷进某种关系里了，而你似乎很擅长结束这种关系。

yingyinNormal.en: Or there is potato city? What's potato city? There's a tour with potato fields ending with a potato tasting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或者是这个土豆城？那什么是土豆城呢？一个可以参观土豆田的旅行，结束时还可以有土豆吃哦。

yingyinNormal.en: Same ending as every day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每天的结局都如出一辙。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you so much. Thank you. Thank you. Yes! What! Happy ending.
yingyinNormal.zh: 非常感谢。谢谢，谢谢。太好了，快乐收场。

yingyinNormal.en: The time of great sorrow was ending. Toruk Macto was no longer needed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 悲痛万分的时候已经过去，托鲁克马托也已不必存在。

yingyinNormal.en: Should've been about Samuel Morse the way they telegraphed that ending.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就那影片的结尾方式[电报] 按理说应该讲萨缪尔·摩尔斯才对。（发明了电报用的摩尔斯电码）

yingyinNormal.en: Well, why don't you make up your own ending? Oh, sure, what a wonderful idea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么不自己编个后续出来呢？行啊，这主意太棒了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm good at ending stories. Granny Pig. And you go downstairs. I won't be long.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很擅长讲故事的结尾，猪奶奶。你先到下面等着吧。我不会太久的。

yingyinNormal.en: For what? What are we going for? Where's the happy ending here? This isn't life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 变成什么?我们到底该怎么办? 怎样才能好好生活? 生活不应该是这样的。

yingyinNormal.en: He inferred that universe ending paradoxes would ensue should he break his promise.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他觉得如果说了那就会使宇宙灭亡。

yingyinNormal.en: Who are you? Eep. Let me clarify, Eep. The world is ending. I'm calling it "The End."
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是谁? 小伊。我来讲讲清楚，小伊，世界要终结了。我把它叫做"剧终"。

yingyinNormal.en: And took all the credit. Oh, yeah. It's my part, the ending. That's what people remember.
yingyinNormal.zh: 并说是你独立创作。是啊，是我写的结局。才是人们记住的部分。

yingyinNormal.en: Use an amount ending in 8, which is particularly lucky in Chinese culture, and avoid the number 4.
yingyinNormal.zh: 数字必须以8结尾，这在中国的文化中被看作是非常幸运的，同时要避免使用4这个数字。

yingyinNormal.en: Because that's what ending with the entitlement you believe you're due. So, you sit. And you think.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为这就是你坚信自己拥有的权利给你带来的下场。所以给我坐下，然后想清楚了。

yingyinNormal.en: I think you slightly gave away the ending. There were five main suspects. One of them called Blessington.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得你好像把答案说漏嘴了。一共五个嫌疑人。其中一个叫布莱辛顿。

yingyinNormal.en: Why not? Well, let's see, first of all, the prospect of ending up bitter and lonely drunk doesn't quite appeal to me. OK.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么不是？嗯，你看，首先，我可不想孤独老死，一人沉醉。好吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, grow up. Hey, I didn't say it. All right, that's enough from the both of you. Well, he started it! Well, I'm ending it!
yingyinNormal.zh: 少幼稚了你！话又不是我说的。够了，你们两个都收声。他先挑事的！那我息事可以了吧！

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. I'm so sorry. I just gave away the ending, didn't I? Oh. It's just, I just heard this story in the cab, and it is all I can think about.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对不起，我说出了结尾，对不对？我在计程车上听了这个故事，满脑子想的都是这个。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, what did Amy tell you? Oh, very well. I can't keep up this clever charade any longer. She told me that you were thinking of ending it with Leonard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，艾米，跟你说什么了？太棒了，你再不猜出来，我也编不出提示了，她告诉我你想跟莱纳德分手。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
